## System
## System: Mainland

## Authority Tier
Primary Statute (Federal Decree-Law No. 42 of 2022)

## Language Variants
Arabic (Mandatory)

## Currency Warning
2022 Reform: Authorized private process servers and electronic notification (SMS/Email).

## Template Type
Court Form - Notification Report (Taqrir I'lan)

## Structural Skeleton
1. Header (Court, Case No.)
2. Details of the Process Server (Bailiff)
3. Details of the Person Notified
4. Method of Notification
5. Outcome (Served/Refused/Absent)
6. Date and Signature

## Drafting Conventions
- Must strictly follow the hierarchy of service methods in the Law.
- Electronic service requires the address to be "verified" or "contractual".

## Fair-Use Excerpt
"The process server hereby confirms that on [Date], the [Document] was notified to the Respondent via [Method]."

## Practical Use
Official record of service in Dubai Mainland Courts.
